+// qinf downstream patch — see qwen-inference/patches/0005-add-deltanet-pre-state-metal.patch
+// Fused pre-state epoxy: l2_norm + tile-repeat for Q and K.
+// src0 = q [head_k_dim, num_k_heads, n_seq_tokens, n_seqs] (may be a strided view)
